Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Crawler
    Crawler is the entry point into our crawling application.
    DOMParser
    DOMParser allows us to take an Object representation of an HTML document and extract a frequency distribution.
    DOMParserTest
    Test to assure that known HTML document fed through DOMParser returns correct frequency distribution
    FrequencyDistribution
    FrequencyDistribution class represents a frequency distribution between words and their count for a given source.
    FrequencyDistributionDAO
    FrequencyDistributionDAO is a data access object that allows us to persist a new frequency distribution.
    Main
    Java Main program to act as client using the Crawler application.
